build: remove obsolete native build artifacts
- Delete .ninja_deps and .ninja_log files for datavein-oracle-native and secure-comm modules. - Remove compiled object files (.o) for crypto_engine.cpp, oracle_drive_jni.cpp, and secure_comm_jni.cpp. - Erase libc++_shared.so from datavein-oracle-native build intermediates.

Update Kotlin standard library and Compose plugin versions
- Updated kotlin("stdlib-jdk8") to specific versions in `collab-canvas`, `secure-comm`, `datavein-oracle-native`, `sandbox-ui`, `feature-module`, `romtools`, and `module-a` build scripts. - Replaced `alias(libs.plugins.kotlin.compose)` with `id("org.jetbrains.kotlin.plugin.compose")` in `secure-comm`, `screenshot-tests`, `sandbox-ui`, and `feature-module` build scripts. - Removed `alias(libs.plugins.compose.compiler)` from `screenshot-tests` and `feature-module` build scripts. - Removed `alias(libs.plugins.kotlin.compose) apply false` from the root `build.gradle.kts`. - Updated `com.squareup.moshi:moshi` from `1.15.0` to `1.15.2` in `app/build.gradle.kts`. - Removed `apply(plugin = "org.jetbrains.compose")` from `sandbox-ui/build.gradle.kts`. - Deleted various .cxx build files.
